701999f-a.title: Bronx: Vyse Avenue - 172nd Street (East)
701999f-a.text:
Vyse Ave., north from and including East 174th Street. The house, at the N.E. corner,bears No. 1764. In the background is visible the elevated structure of the I.R.T. Bronx Park subway line.
1917.
